title: KYLE - iSpy feat. Lil Yachty (2017)
description: The "iSpy" music video by KYLE featuring Lil Yachty combines playful animation with live-action, creating a whimsical and colorful world that reflects the song's lighthearted vibe. It transports the viewer into a carefree, imaginative space where the artists, portrayed as children, explore vibrant, animated landscapes. This creative blend of elements highlights the song's themes of joy and escapism.
